{"tid":997911,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍城廣場麥當勞屌你老母","createTime":"2019-01-27T14:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T14:06:07.000Z","uid":11127,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"946074ad11b2d139746b86a06e439aae2642e1a3","tid":997911,"uid":11127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"雖然冇飲筒，不過現實啲講老麥真係平，咁去食啦，<br />\n我唔係住九龍城，但要去做野，打算喺嗰度快食個餐。<br />\n入到去見到已經好多人等緊攞餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過太耐冇食老麥諗住食脆香雞翼就喺機買，<br />\n跟住坐低等，我足足等左25分鐘先有得攞，<br />\n廿鳩幾張單得兩丁友出餐，想點撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喂你唔係快餐店黎嘅咩，屌你要我等半粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好喇算啦有得食，跟住有個執盤阿姐，<br />\n應該係殘疾嘅唔知邊方面，其實我明白你地要<br />\n做下樣請下呢類人扮下平等待遇，咁我冇問題。<br />\n最大問題係佢有浸尿味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要喺我張枱附近<br />\n周圍行，咁臭我點食野呀，以為自己喺公廁食緊薯條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我都忍你，我閉氣食快快脆走人，<br />\n點知跟住你成架垃圾車擺喺個lobby到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我喺啲垃圾隔離食野係咩情況，屌你咩<br />\n仲要突然有個智障仔走埋黎問我野，<br />\n嚇到我鳩都縮，唔緊要我知唔關你地事，<br />\n間間老麥都有呢啲人，仲要大半間都係大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入面嗰浸酸縮味臭到，又要焗住，<br />\n加埋啲賓賓除鞋細路周圍走大叫。<br />\n真係唔會再黎呢間麥當勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa11d8e40ab7d61e8e1f7a8d5417981b3fe0e91","tid":997911,"uid":68457,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:04:15.000Z","msg":"全線麥當勞都要ban啦 認真"},{"pid":"db9c7fbf01e493fa6445cc84f381890d3adc2238","tid":997911,"uid":11127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4aa11d8e40ab7d61e8e1f7a8d5417981b3fe0e91","tid":997911,"uid":68457,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:04:15.000Z","msg":"全線麥當勞都要ban啦 認真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:04:46.000Z","msg":"唔會再去呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2854a3c8498afcd78efcd5eaf6bae0e5d38565c8","tid":997911,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:05:03.000Z","msg":"有無TL;DR"},{"pid":"b5d422caaee0720df80a195774dbce4ba113230b","tid":997911,"uid":11127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2854a3c8498afcd78efcd5eaf6bae0e5d38565c8","tid":997911,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:05:03.000Z","msg":"有無TL;DR"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:06:07.000Z","msg":"咁都too long<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}